data.description: Pristine, spacious, and lovely semi-track home in the cozy Rosabella community on Alexander. PERFECT for quick access to Nellis Air Force Base. This home features 3 bedrooms - 3 bathrooms- and a 2 car garage. The kitchen comes with a highly desired island, ample counterspace, and lovely stainless steel appliances. The living room area has gorgeous vinyl flooring, a dining area, and a nook that could double as a den or office. Upstairs is equipped with a spacious loft/living area.
